      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in truly mint condition\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this car from day one, keeping it spotless and perfectly maintained inside and out. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you definitely won't be disappointed!",
