    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This pristine example features a high-revving, naturally aspirated flat-six mated to a precise six-speed manual transaxle. The chassis dynamics are sharpened by a factory-tuned multi-link rear suspension and a mechanical limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal power delivery through the apex. Every component, from the cross-drilled rotors to the forged alloy wheels, remains in concours-level state. With negligible mechanical wear and a perfectly linear torque curve, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of analog driver engagement and engineering integrity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
